result.name: Victoria Harbour Roasted Goose Seafood Restaurant

reviews.text:
Seriously good roast goose! If you're in the Ma On Shan and itching for this dish, this place will satisfy. 

We also ordered the sweet and sour pork, and the wagyu beef cubes. Both were very good as well. 

The only let down was the difficulty on getting the attention of the serving staff. I had to wave my upraised hand for 3 mins before I got any service.
Cozy restaurant, delicious roast goose, recommend
Dim sum is not as good as the Sheung Shui shop
Very good for dinner.  Nice Chinese food. The goose is very tasty and famous.
Discounted dim sum after 2PM.  The food is very decent.  Will viw again.

以連鎖式酒樓來說，它是最好的，食物口味可以，價格大眾化。每次光顧必點燒鵝👍🏻
